<Schematic Name="3PDT true bypass pedal" Description="Single-transistor BJT boost wrapped in a 3PDT footswitch. Pole 1 routes input, pole 2 routes output, pole 3 grounds the LED only when the effect is engaged. 9V battery and +9V DC rail." PartNumber="">
